T1  - Seasonalities in NYSE Bid-Ask Spreads and Stock Returns in January
AU  - CLARK, ROBERT A.
AU  - McCONNELL, JOHN J.
AU  - SINGH, MANOJ
Y1  - 1992/12/01
PY  - 1992
DA  - 1992/12/01
